I've used that stuff before, and variations thereof.  It works OK in
terms of muffling the sound, but there are concerns about condensation.
Alternately, take a look at this stuff.  Dampesn the sound well, and
doesn't absorb water.

http://vintagebus.com/cgi-bin/search.cgi?string=mcmaster

